message.body: Hey crazy, miss you at the circus!
Martha! You're back! What are you doing now?
Matching tiny numbers on one sheet to tiny numbers on another sheet. :) let's get lunch sometime, o hear you're downtown
I love matching tiny numbers. You are quite the detective/spy so I doubt you'll run into any trouble. Are you in Minneapolis? Yes, let's do lunch.
Im in MPLS and back at Medfinance matching numbers... Hahaha not funny at all. But yes. We can go to target together too...
What!? You're back at Medfinance? Crazy. I bet that place is really fun without me or Sarah around. Regina's still there, right?
Yes thank god. She's the one that got then to offer me a position. Otherwise it's prettyttttty quiet.
I think you, me, Sarah, Regina, and whoever else should do a happy hour some time.
Yes yes yes. Make it happen Kampa
